   * Default light: #0845BF → #006EE7 → #4F90EE at 0% / 60% / 100%
   * No 1px border (avoids subpixel gaps vs rounded gradient). No accent-colored shadow blur
   * (that reads as a “ring” on dark UI); depth uses token shadow only.
   */
  .h-btn--elevated {
    border: 0;
    padding: calc(0.7rem + 1px) calc(1.5rem + 1px);
    background: linear-gradient(to top right, #0845bf 0%, #006ee7 60%, #4f90ee 100%);
    color: var(--prism-color-text-on-accent);
